reviewText: Not as good as the earlier DooWop dvds as there were not many different acts - but it was enjoyable
GREAT MUSIC THAT CAN NOW BE ENJOYED BY WATCHING THE ACTUAL PERFORMANCES.

A big rip off. It's not a reunion. These are clips from the TV show ROCK AND ROLL PALACE with host WOLFMAN JACK. The quality is unbelievable. Very OUT OF FOCUS - NO CONTRAST. pretty much UNWATCHABLE. Can I get a refund for false advertising? Full frame as well.
Was not what i expected,a little dissappointing. Thought there would be more musical groups in the concert.
